snippet.title: Animal Arena - App Preview
snippet.description: Animal Arena is a wacky arena battle game for 1-4 players featuring cute animals and simple one button controls. Fight across unique arenas, collect weapon power-ups, and stomp opponents to win! Earn points by battling to unlock more playable animals!
